snippet.title: Chris Stapleton, Miranda Lambert - Maggie's Song (ACM Awards 2021) ft. Miranda Lambert
snippet.description:
Chris Stapleton performs, “Maggie's Song” with Miranda Lambert live from the 56th Academy of Country Music Awards.

 

Listen to Chris Stapleton’s album, 'Starting Over' out now - http://strm.to/CSStartingOverAlbum

 

To support or adopt a shelter pet, visit Miranda Lambert’s foundation MuttNation.com 

 

Listen to Chris Stapleton’s latest music: http://strm.to/chrisstapletonmusic
